= Ascending sort for Balatro

Click a sort button again to switch between ascending and descending.
You can also set your preferred sort as default.

== Preview

image::preview.webp[]

== Installation

Install the same way you installed steamodded

=== without Steamodded

This mod only needs steamodded to set new default sort.
You can just download the lovely.toml and place it in a directory in your mods folder.

